    "speaker": {
      "display_name": "Renato Valdes Olmos",
      "matched_calendar_invitee_email": "renato@growthx.ai"
    },
    "text": "And these grid systems, I think, provide a very great way to lay out information-dense things like the ones you provided in a way that's still very aesthetically pleasing.",
